## 1. Primary user flow (decision tree)

```mermaid
flowchart TB
  subgraph entry["Landing"]
    A[Landing / Hero]
  end

  A --> B[Buy Now]
  A --> C[Watch Video]
  A --> D[Scroll to explore]

  D --> E[Features]
  E --> F[Accessories — In the Box]
  F --> G[Products — MoGo 4 vs Pro]
  G --> H[Platform rating]
  H --> I[Newsletter]

  G --> B2[Buy Now — product card]
  B --> J[(XGIMI store — external)]
  B2 --> J

  I --> K[Subscribe success]
```

## 2. Linear scroll journey (same page)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  H[Header sticky] --- O[Overview Hero]
  O --- FE[Features]
  FE --- AC[Accessories]
  AC --- PR[Products]
  PR --- RA[Platform rating]
  RA --- NW[Newsletter]
  NW --- FT[Footer]
```

## 3. Conversion funnel (simplified)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  V[Visitors] --> E[Engaged scroll 25%+]
  E --> P[Reached Products]
  P --> C{Conversion}
  C -->|Buy| X[External checkout]
  C -->|Lead| N[Newsletter signup]
```

## 4. Swimlane (user / page / external)

```mermaid
flowchart TB
  subgraph user["User"]
    U1[Arrives]
    U2[Scrolls / clicks nav]
    U3[Clicks Buy or Subscribe]
  end

  subgraph page["Landing page"]
    P1[Hero + sections]
    P2[Anchor scroll]
    P3[Forms + links]
  end

  subgraph external["External"]
    E1[XGIMI eu.xgimi.com]
    E2[Mailchimp / email]
  end

  U1 --> P1
  U2 --> P2
  U3 --> P3
  P3 --> E1
  P3 --> E2
```
